with mock.patch.object(cv2, 'VideoCapture', new_callable=mock.MagicMock
    ) as mock_cv_capture:
    cap = mock.MagicMock()
    cap.isOpened.return_value = True
    cap_end = mock.MagicMock()
    cap_end.isOpened.return_value = False
    mock_cv_capture.side_effect = [cap, cap, cap, cap_end]
    ids = gfi.get_cam_ids()
    assert ids == [0, 1, 2]
